Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然帶陌生人回來 嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\be3\blur3\an8\fs26}翻譯 明撒 童話 天井 校譯 茶 時間 茶 後期 DK 壓制 A4
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:05:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界裏 有好多過著普通生活的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥在最前線的我們 要對這些人負起責呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直認為變強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為把自己的生命放在了第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在有很多的人 都期待著桐人君呢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也包括我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我保證過會救大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 至少再稍稍給我們點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs32}加油！西田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs32}把湖主釣上來！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來大家都知道有湖主這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們今天的主要活動即將要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們好等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人先生 拜託你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底會是多大的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…已經上鉤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西 西田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 上鉤了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切…切換
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這個混蛋！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 能行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人 很危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太…太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要只是自己一個人逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在陸地上跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肺魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\fad(500,500)}肺魚:硬骨魚類的一個類群的魚，頜為自接式，平時用鰓呼吸，在乾涸時可以用鰾當作肺呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人先生 現在可不是說這些的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人夫人 快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人先生 你夫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人夫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲…厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亞絲娜小姐吧 怎麼會在這裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的粉絲 跟我握一下手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希茲克利夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 不要磨蹭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 才兩個星期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連在休假中的我們都被召集到前線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是發生了相當嚴重的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少去聽聽是什麼事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾下弄完再回來就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你來送我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:41.36,biaoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be2\blur3\pos(512,503)}2024年11月7日 第22層·克拉魯 轉移門廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是很短暫的時間 但很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏哪裏 是很寶貴的體驗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實在見到兩位之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直認為攻略遊戲那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本是我們不同的另一個次元的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被困在這個世界2年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使現在能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能回到公司去也不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裏也許已經放棄從這裏出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的出不去了 就一直在這裏釣魚好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很慚愧的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最初也有同樣的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天晚上都一個人在那裏哭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺每在這個世界過一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的現實世界都在漸漸地崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在最後 我決定去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得勝利 勇往直前 總之只想著要變強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在廣場的草坪上發現了睡午覺的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時怒氣生頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣的說到「不要浪費時間」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那人卻回駁到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:11:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「今天是艾恩葛朗特的最好的季節 而且還是最好的氣候設定」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「這麼好的日子去攻略迷宮 太可惜了」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也試著在草坪上躺下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉沉的睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來後 已經是傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還擺出了一副呆呆的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣和他一起組隊之間  我察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就算是在這樣的世界 也在好好的活著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在浪費現實的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是在這裏一點一點積累著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些告訴我的 就是這位桐人君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要想著他的事睡覺 就不會做惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得很期待見他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭一次覺得 能到這裏來 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人君對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我在這裏生活這2年的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是活著的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是為了和這個人相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 才戴上了NERvGear
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西田先生 你也一定有重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以捨棄自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是可以捨棄的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然幫不了你們什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次 再一起釣魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉移 古蘭扎姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:56.43,biaoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\be2\blur3\pos(512,503)}2024年11月7日 第55層·古蘭扎姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵察隊全滅了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了即將到來的BOSS戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派出了5個公會聯合組成的 共20人的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 最前面的10人到達房間的中央後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BOSS出現的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口的門就關閉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉移水晶 無效化的區域啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 5分鐘後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於門打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間裏什麼都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10個人和BOSS一起消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算這樣 我們也決不能放棄攻略
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有盡可能的以大部隊來挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來協助你吧 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我來說 亞絲娜的安全是最優先的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果陷入了危機 比起隊伍全體的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會優先保護她的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保護什麼的人是很強的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的勇戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有三小時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了不要生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的BOSS攻略戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要參加 就在這裏等我好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼說這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能使用轉移水晶的地方 不知道會發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有個三長兩短…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己一個人去如此危險的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我在安全的地方等待麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果桐人君沒有回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…會自殺的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經沒有活著的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且無法原諒只是等待著的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我膽怯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心裏只想著逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算回不到現實世界也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那個森林的小屋裏 一直兩人生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 如果能這樣 很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天 一起 任何時候都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人君考慮過麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現實的身體 變得怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個遊戲開始  才幾周時候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎所有的玩家 都發生了幾個小時的斷線事件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 大概那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的玩家都被移動到了各地的醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們的身體是在醫院的病床上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用什麼方法存活的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是這樣 你以為最多能夠撐幾年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與遊戲能否通關無關
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:16:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是存在限制時間的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一輩子都跟桐人君在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真的交往
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正地結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起慢慢變老
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 不得不去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:37.98,biaoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\be2\blur3\pos(512,503)}第75層 科利尼亞 轉移門廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你們也參加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要這麼驚訝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是連生意都不顧跑來助陣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法理解我這無私無慾的高貴情操嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 戰利品的分配就沒你的份了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不啊啊 那個可…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迴廊 打開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種討厭的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們血盟騎士團作為前鋒阻擋攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家在這期間盡可能地看穿攻擊模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從而靈活地反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會是一場嚴酷的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我相信諸位的能力足以衝破困境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了解放的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人君由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 桐人君也要保護我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在靠今天的戰利品大賺一筆前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒發生啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skull…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髏收割者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(512,518)}<Skull Reaper>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別聚在一起 快點散開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…就用了一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太變態了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣根本連靠近都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人同時接下攻擊的話 能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來擋住鐮刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家從側面攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太猖狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:29.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠くに聞こえた　鐘の音が少し寂しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:29.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從遠處傳來的鐘聲 傳達著淡淡的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:34.36,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一度強く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:34.36,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次地努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:41.79,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今度は高く　駆け抜けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:41.79,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定能達到更高的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:47.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただ繰り返す現実も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:47.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是在無限反覆著的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:53.68,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}星の数の願い事も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:53.68,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}還是那些如同繁星般多的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:58.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}目指すべき明日を見つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:58.89,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}在找到前進方向的我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:04.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}この想いには勝てない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:04.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}全都戰勝不了這份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:11.10,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}目の前に開かれた果てない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:11.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}在眼前無限延伸的這沒有盡頭的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:15.21,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}たとえ仮想でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:15.21,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}即使是夢也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:18.18,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}迷い続けても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:18.18,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}就算會一直迷路下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:22.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}夢の奥で強く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:22.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}只要能在這夢中變強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:27.96,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}ずっと　ずっと　響いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:27.96,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}願此思念 永遠響徹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:34.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}そっと　そっと　光ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:34.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}願此思念 永遠閃耀
